1
00:00:06,719 --> 00:00:07,320
Hey, hey, hey!

2
00:00:08,359 --> 00:00:09,279
What are you doing?

3
00:00:12,919 --> 00:00:14,400
I set my GPS for Lingshan Lake,

4
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:15,720
and it brought me here.

5
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:16,480
Can I get through this way?

6
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:17,879
This is a Private Club.

7
00:00:17,960 --> 00:00:18,640
You can't get through.

8
00:00:19,079 --> 00:00:20,679
Go forward, there's a fork ahead.

9
00:00:22,079 --> 00:00:24,239
That's not right. I came from this road.

10
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,679
I didn't see any fork.

11
00:00:26,039 --> 00:00:27,600
Turn back. You can't get through here.

12
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:31,079
Alright, thanks.

13
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,799
Comrades,

14
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:15,120
after days and nights of relentless

15
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,239
and arduous effort from everyone,

16
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,799
the serial rape-murder ringleader Ma Shijiang

17
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,280
was shot dead on the spot.

18
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:22,239
The case is officially closed.

19
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,359
Chief Xing,

20
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,560
the mastermind who uploaded the crime videos

21
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,439
hasn't been caught yet.

22
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:33,040
We can't rush this.

23
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,680
The tech team is on it around the clock.

24
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,400
Comrades,

25
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:49,719
I know everyone is deeply saddened.

26
00:01:51,879 --> 00:01:53,799
We feel exactly the same way.

27
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,680
Comrade Zhao Qingming's tragic sacrifice

28
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:04,120
came at an extremely painful cost.

29
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,760
With his own life,

30
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,759
he safeguarded the people's peace

31
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,280
and embodied the honor of a police officer.

32
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:16,919
What he left behind for us

33
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,960
is the conviction of a detective.

34
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,680
So,

35
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,719
we must pull ourselves together,

36
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,919
take Comrade Qingming as our role model,

37
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:31,120
and follow the path

38
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,280
he paved for us with his blood,

39
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,479
marching firmly onward

40
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:38,400
in the fight against crime.

41
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,240
Understood?

42
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:42,439
Yes, sir. Understood.

43
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:43,919
Louder!

44
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,280
Understood! Yes, sir!

45
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,639
One more announcement.

46
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,439
Go ahead and announce it.

47
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,120
Comrade Wang Yonglin

48
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:56,240
is officially appointed Captain of the

49
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,400
Fengdu Major Crimes Unit.

50
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,240
Proceed with the handover.

51
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:00,879
Let's welcome him.

52
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:03,360
Good, good.

53
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,879
Be upright as a person,

54
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,240
be tough in your work,

55
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,280
be precise in cases,

56
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:28,240
and always keep the people in your heart.

57
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:43,360
From now on, we must all work together.

58
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,400
We must take our Major Crimes Unit's

59
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,840
spirit of hard work

60
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,360
and bravery in cracking major cases,

61
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:49,800
and carry it forward.

62
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,919
We cracked a major case,

63
00:03:53,479 --> 00:03:54,599
and got commended for it.

64
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:57,759
We really should celebrate.

65
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,319
How about this:

66
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,120
Tonight, my treat, the whole team,

67
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,520
spicy hot pot.

68
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,120
How about it?

69
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:05,879
Great, great.

70
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:10,479
Um, Captain Wang,

71
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,759
I'll go tidy up the office for you.

72
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,719
Fang Ping.

73
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,680
Yes, Captain Li?

74
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,439
I'll pack up my Boss's things myself.

75
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,839
Captain Li, you really don't have to.

76
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:25,240
I'll just go and tidy it up...

77
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,680
Did you not hear me?

78
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,439
Yes, sir.

79
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,160
Captain Li,

80
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,639
let me help you.

81
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,199
Li Kaiyang!

82
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:43,439
Why are you taking it out on everyone?

83
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,720
You think you're the only one grieving Captain Zhao?

84
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,480
Let me tell you,

85
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:52,160
every single person here is heartbroken.

86
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:54,800
But life has to go on.

87
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,079
I said I'd pack up my Boss's things myself.

88
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,160
Did you not hear me?

89
00:04:59,079 --> 00:04:59,920
What's that supposed to mean?

90
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,600
Did you not hear me?

91
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:05,560
Li Kaiyang!

92
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,959
Get over here.

93
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:18,639
You think only you were like a brother to Qingming?

94
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,319
You think only you are cut to the bone by his death?

95
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,399
Have you asked anyone else?

96
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,639
Every one of us, just like you,

97
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,439
is devastated by grief.

98
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,439
But don't forget,

99
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,399
we are the people's police.

100
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:43,000
We can't keep drowning in our grief.

101
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:44,319
I hope everyone

102
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:49,120
will carry their endless memories of Qingming,

103
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:52,399
handle every case well,

104
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,199
and build them into rock-solid cases,

105
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,199
to honor the heroic spirit of Comrade Qingming.

106
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:13,399
Wipe away your tears.

107
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:16,879
Go on.

108
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,079
Be upright as a person,

109
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,399
be tough in your work,

110
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:32,279
be precise in cases,

111
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,399
and always keep the people in your heart.

112
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,079
Boss.

113
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,639
I'll remember every word you said.

114
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,120
I promise you,

115
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,759
as long as I'm still alive,

116
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,199
I will see this case through to the end.

117
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,160
Boss

118
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,480
I brought your stuff back for you.

119
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,759
Just work from home for now.

120
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,680
It's quiet here.

121
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:50,759
No one can disturb you.

122
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,080
Boss.

123
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,480
You suspect Ma Shijiang's death is suspicious?

124
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,600
And Captain Zhao's death too.

125
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,519
But we saw Captain Zhao's death with our own eyes.

126
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:42,919
Did you actually see Ma Shijiang kill him?

127
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,440
Big Liu said so himself.

128
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,679
You think he's lying?

129
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,080
I can't piece it together yet.

130
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:54,639
But I feel like I'm looking at a massive black hole.

131
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,720
And it's bottomless.

132
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,679
Boss.

133
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,639
Aren't you being overly suspicious?

134
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,200
Ma Shijiang killed Captain Zhao.

135
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,639
Big Liu shot Ma Shijiang dead.

136
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:05,080
The unit already investigated all of this.

137
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:06,320
There's nothing suspicious to follow up on.

138
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,559
I found this at Captain Zhao's house.

139
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,120
Before he went to arrest Ma Shijiang,

140
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,240
he'd been investigating in secret.

141
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,600
A Private Club.

142
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,279
This location...

143
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,120
is right near where Ma Shijiang vanished.

144
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,159
Whose club is it?

145
00:09:28,399 --> 00:09:30,000
I haven't had the chance to look into it yet.

146
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:32,000
For Ma Shijiang to disappear that night

147
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,480
completely unnoticed,

148
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,480
someone must have helped him.

149
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:37,720
The fact that Captain Zhao marked this place

150
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,840
means he'd already figured out

151
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,440
the connection between Ma Shijiang and this club.

152
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,519
He just ran out of time.

153
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,279
Boss,

154
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,759
please stop grieving.

155
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,320
What we need to do now

156
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:57,000
is report these leads up the chain right away.

157
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,600
The Ma Shijiang case can't be closed yet.

158
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,559
Without solid evidence to back it up,

159
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,240
it's all just speculation on our part.

160
00:10:05,279 --> 00:10:06,080
Besides...

161
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,559
What are you worried about?

162
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,879
I'm worried that

163
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,039
we're out in the open, while our enemy is hidden.

164
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:13,919
If he had the power

165
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:16,240
to cut off the leads before we reached the truth,

166
00:10:16,799 --> 00:10:18,399
then he can certainly destroy the evidence too.

167
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:21,000
Just like the Red Gloves back then.

168
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,200
Vanished without a single trace.

169
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,000
Boss,

170
00:10:27,639 --> 00:10:30,080
were the Red Gloves really that terrifying?

171
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,159
I'll explain that to you later.

172
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:37,559
No matter what,

173
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:40,639
we have to dig out the secrets

174
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:41,519
hidden behind Ma Shijiang.

175
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,799
We need to find out if he and the Red Gloves

176
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:45,000
actually had any connection.

177
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:48,519
Jiang Han.

178
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,519
Head over to the Economic Crimes Unit.

179
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:51,320
Go find Li Ai.

180
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,240
You know her pretty well.

181
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:53,960
Go through it carefully with her,

182
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,519
all of Ma Shijiang's financial transactions.

183
00:10:56,159 --> 00:10:57,799
Maybe we'll uncover something useful.

184
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,879
I'll go right now.

185
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,360
Jiang Han.

186
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:02,360
What we just discussed,

187
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:04,600
only two people in this world can know.

188
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,200
What can't be said over the phone?

189
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,200
That we have to meet so secretly in a car?

190
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,120
Well, it's been a while since I've seen

191
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,480
the prettiest girl in the Economic Crimes Unit.

192
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:36,240
Hey, stop right there.

193
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,200
Just get to the point.

194
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,279
Don't say things you don't mean.

195
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,559
I need you to look someone up.

196
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,799
Here's the assist request and the file.

197
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,200
If that's all,

198
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:44,960
I'm leaving.

199
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:46,799
Hey, aren't you even gonna look?

200
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:47,759
Agreeing so readily.

201
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:49,480
You want me to turn you down?

202
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:53,039
A few days apart and you've learned to talk back?

203
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,799
Well, I have you to thank for that.

204
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,559
If you keep using me when convenient

205
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:57,720
and tossing me aside when you don't,

206
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,519
talking back will be the least of it.

207
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:00,200
Alright.

208
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:01,759
I, Jiang, wouldn't dare step out of line.

209
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,919
That's more like it.

210
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:04,039
See you at 10 p.m.

211
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,159
Hey, hey, hey!

212
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,000
What are you doing?

213
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:18,159
I set my GPS for Lingshan Lake,

214
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:19,399
and it brought me here.

215
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,200
Can I get through this way?

216
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:22,279
This is a Private Club. You can't get through.

217
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,600
Alright, thanks.

218
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:55,960
Ruolan.

219
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,120
Don't be afraid.

220
00:12:57,639 --> 00:12:58,279
It's me.

221
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:03,679
Sit down.

222
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:15,240
This doll is from Ming Liang, isn't it?

223
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:22,039
That kid is truly devoted to you.

224
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,080
Li.

225
00:13:23,759 --> 00:13:24,399
Yeah.

226
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,840
Is my brother really gone?

227
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,080
He...

228
00:13:37,399 --> 00:13:39,559
He's just protecting you in a different way.

229
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:46,440
I keep seeing him.

230
00:13:49,919 --> 00:13:52,120
Standing at the end of the hallway, smiling at me.

231
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:56,039
Just like when he was alive.

232
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,279
Only he looks a bit more worn out.

233
00:14:01,919 --> 00:14:02,639
Li.

234
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:05,360
They say people who've passed away

235
00:14:07,799 --> 00:14:09,360
become stars in the sky,

236
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,799
watching over the ones they love.

237
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:15,279
Do you believe that?

238
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:17,879
Of course.

239
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,519
You're the one he loved most.

240
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:25,080
He'll surely become a star to watch over you.

241
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:45,240
Ma Shijiang's account has frequent transactions.

242
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:47,519
I've flagged several suspicious people for you.

243
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,559
The larger transactions

244
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,159
were with this person.

245
00:14:53,279 --> 00:14:54,200
Shen Qing.

246
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:56,879
Why does that name sound familiar?

247
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,840
Shen Qing is involved in a major loan fraud case.

248
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,559
Economic Crimes is investigating her.

249
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,799
What a coincidence.

250
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,960
What's her background?

251
00:15:05,679 --> 00:15:07,600
Head of the loan department at Fengdu Bank.

252
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,320
I need to send this info to Boss right away.

253
00:15:38,919 --> 00:15:40,080
Liu Xiang's best friend,

254
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:41,600
Shen Qing.

255
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,159
Done eating? Let's go.

256
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,559
Welcome.

257
00:16:11,559 --> 00:16:13,080
The menu's on the wall.

258
00:16:13,519 --> 00:16:14,240
Shredded pork noodles.

259
00:16:14,639 --> 00:16:15,840
Extra chili sauce, extra vinegar.

260
00:16:17,279 --> 00:16:17,960
Captain Li.

261
00:16:18,679 --> 00:16:19,639
Come in, come in.

262
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:22,080
Big Liu, Captain Li's here.

263
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:23,639
Big Liu.

264
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:28,080
Captain Li.

265
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:29,960
I left in such a rush back then,

266
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,080
I didn't even come to see you.

267
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,240
Hey, honey.

268
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:33,559
Go make Captain Li some noodles.

269
00:16:33,679 --> 00:16:34,240
Okay.

270
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,279
Come on, sit down.

271
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,840
Why'd you resign in such a hurry?

272
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:47,120
I failed to protect Captain Zhao.

273
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:49,919
I can't face any of you.

274
00:16:50,159 --> 00:16:50,919
It's not your fault.

275
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,279
Don't blame yourself too much.

276
00:16:54,759 --> 00:16:56,000
There's no need to leave the force.

277
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:58,039
Take some time to rest.

278
00:16:58,919 --> 00:16:59,879
Come back in a few days.

279
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:03,240
I've already made up my mind.

280
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:06,160
My kid's illness needs money.

281
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,200
Business here is pretty good.

